61
00:10:23,975 --> 00:10:26,094
Te veré atrás.

62
00:10:37,612 --> 00:10:41,567
- ¿Lo tienes?
- Sí. ¿Y tú?

63
00:10:42,242 --> 00:10:43,504
Cassie Lockhart.

64
00:10:43,617 --> 00:10:45,716
